  "body": "According to the current definiton, the instruction BYTE sets the most significant byte.\r\nHowever implementations set the least significant byte (which makes more sense):\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/33d233d3e18359123993d3f54987441290faf212/core/vm/instructions.go#L291\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/aleth/blob/ec3886029393fc9927b130ba8f8671480d810391/libaleth-interpreter/VM.cpp#L728\r\nhttps://github.com/paritytech/parity-ethereum/blob/7c335e87642b848f61ab3ee7bbff5964b53d6f11/ethcore/evm/src/interpreter/mod.rs#L1001",
